headline: EOG Resources to Present at Upcoming Conference
summary: EOG Resources, Inc. (EOG) is scheduled to present at the Barclays CEO Energy-Power Conference at 1:25 p.m. Central time (2:25 p.m. Eastern time) on Tuesday, September 2. Ezra Y. Yacob, Chairman and Chief Executive Officer, will present on behalf of EOG.
